cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI. 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to analyze conversational dependencies between messages in online chat. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses probabilistic classifiers, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses semantic information, which is related to cs.LG (Learning) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
